project_descr:
"Sustainable Agriculture in the Autonomous Republic of Ajara".
Objective: to support the establishment of mechanism for sustainable and effective agriculture in the Autonomous Republic of Ajara.

outputs.output_descr: 1/ improve the quality/results of extension services for farmers; 2/ increase the productivity and commercial effectiveness of farmers/cooperatives by creating high value supply chain in agriculture  sector, 3/ strengthen institutionally  MoAgriculture
